<title>mn ly swạk yḥmyny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mn ly swạk yḥmyny mn kl sẖr qạỷm)2
 mn ly swạk yrwyny mn kl nbʿiⁿ fạỷḍ
 ạlqrạr - (ạ̉nt ạ̹lhy lạ swạk ạ̉nt ạ̹lhy lạ swạk)2
 2- (mn ly swạk sydy ymlạ̉ frạgẖ wḥdty)2
 mn ly swạk mrsẖdy yhms ly fy kẖlwty
 3- (kyf ạ̉kẖạf fy ạlṭryq wạ̉nt ly nbʿ ạlrjạʾ)2 kyf bdwnk ạ̉syr fy ʿạlm blạ ʿzạʾ
 4- (ậty ạ̹lyk ḍạrʿạaⁿ fạ̉nẓr ạ̹ly mn ʿlạk)2
 ạ̉nẓr ạ̹ly sạndạaⁿ ḥty ạ̉ʿysẖ fy rḍạk</lyrics>
</song>